review_text: Small park just outside Côte Vertu metro station. There's a playground and swings for young kids. It's reasonably clean and alright for a picnic.

(Translated by Google) A beautiful park is it's good to go from the Cote-Virtue station to Cardinal Street.

But a lot of smokers.

Not bad.

(Original)
Un beaux parc est c'est bien d'aller de la station Cote-vertu vers la rue Cardinal.

Mais beaucoup de fumeurs.

Pas mal.

(Translated by Google) Too small. And no one respects the non-smoking policy. It even looks like a smoker's club

(Original)
Trop petit. Et personne ne respecte la consigne de non fumeur. On dirait même que c'est un club pour fumeur
